Guasdualito that Venezuela's armed forces would repel any 
incursions across the border. 
</P>
<P>
	Colombian rebels often cross the Venezuelan border to kidnap and  
extort Venezuelan ranchers and businessmen. Colombian troops 
sometimes pursue them. 
</P>
